    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/5705e4905391eb3a21500223df193865.poster.avif?t=1761726096\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/5705e4905391eb3a21500223df193865.webm?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/5705e4905391eb3a21500223df193865.mp4?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《Red Tether》的特色在于俯视角的激烈太空动作和别具一格的“间接战斗”系统。面对浩渺的太空舰队和剧烈对抗，你将以牵引标枪和聪明才智应对。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/12070cb14aac4c106b0865cdaffed6fc.poster.avif?t=1761726096\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/12070cb14aac4c106b0865cdaffed6fc.webm?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/12070cb14aac4c106b0865cdaffed6fc.mp4?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进行以牵引为核心的太空战，战斗核心在于连接敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用可伸缩的牵引标枪让敌舰相互撞击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精准部署标枪，撕下敌方武器和附属装备。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用抓钩绕过障碍灵活移动，巧妙躲避敌舰。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把你的飞船当作冲锋舰，勇猛地冲撞敌人。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/e5f0ae8ae7221d46f0614556e5c03b6d.poster.avif?t=1761726096\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/e5f0ae8ae7221d46f0614556e5c03b6d.webm?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/e5f0ae8ae7221d46f0614556e5c03b6d.mp4?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验新颖的“战斗解谜”游戏玩法，在快速行动中迅速做出战术决策。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心策划如何运用舰船制敌，选择合适的时机解除武装或摧毁敌舰，并巧妙利用瞬息万变的战场。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习应对各种舰队组成，包括攻击舰、支援舰和后勤单位。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在50多种预设波次中战斗，或在无尽模式下面对随机生成的舰队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与超过16个强大的首领敌人交锋，并将它们转化成壮观的爆炸。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵活躲避敌人明显的攻击，并将其反转为对敌人的攻势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规避或利用各种战场隐患，如燃油泄漏、带电船壳、冷却云和磁场等。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/1b838f6b1c01b468e2da3c54a4db6670.poster.avif?t=1761726096\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/1b838f6b1c01b468e2da3c54a4db6670.webm?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/1b838f6b1c01b468e2da3c54a4db6670.mp4?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁超过18种独具特色的玩家飞船，每种都会带来不同的游玩风格、优势和挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用超过120种可组合的飞船和牵引升级来完善你的飞船。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕捉并收集14种生物机械鱼，获取尖端技术。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索10多个星系区域以及其中的新敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集飞船残骸中的黑匣子，逐渐了解游戏的剧情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞥见这个复杂科幻宇宙的一隅，与 Hyperspace Dogfights 和 Swirl W@tch 同一世界观。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁多种游戏后期的挑战模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持游戏手柄和辅助选项。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/59466e93fe1ba8d7c0aff4a2cd20b985.poster.avif?t=1761726096\" width=480 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/59466e93fe1ba8d7c0aff4a2cd20b985.webm?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714080/extras/59466e93fe1ba8d7c0aff4a2cd20b985.mp4?t=1761726096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
